            <div class="title">
                The War At Sea
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1939-11-08/debates/644b4682-8fd5-4d6a-ad18-a61b6a6143df/NationalLoans" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
